metadata.description:
LNRZ ON SOUND WK 8

Is that a bird? Is it a plane? Nah, it's Wes Period floating down from the sky to deliver BARS. 

A note from Wes himself:

"Really was just on my shit talking vibe tbh. Somedays you wake up, turn the swag on, and just one bar out! It was one of those days lol. I’m pretty sure at one point I thought to myself “Who tf do I think I am?!” my dude Tim Randolph and I cooked something up and ran with it."
